comments.content: The upper left capitals look like **[Super Grotesk Condensed Medium](http://web.archive.org/web/20150415025700/http:/www.findmyfont.com/index.php/fonts/font-preview?fset=FontShop%20%2F%20%28Commercial%29&ffam=SuperGroteskA%20CdMedLF%20-%20Regular&fid=56fab68f54deac617c204bd6b52bd262&fsize=60&text=ASTER%20AGE%20UD&wrap=2)** while the lowercase must be **[Neuzeit Book Heavy](http://web.archive.org/web/20150415025700/http:/www.findmyfont.com/index.php/fonts/font-preview?fset=Linotype%20%2F%20%28Commercial%29&ffam=Neuzeit%20S%20LT%20BookHeavy%20-%20Regular&fid=5eace809f31c88ceb8d8b6e75f577dd0&fsize=48&text=means%20claimed.%20In%20this%20society%20reaches%20a.%20As%20we%20stare%20deskilled%20caught&wrap=2)**
